<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lexend">
  <style>
    :root {
      --color-black: #101524;
    }

    *,
    *:after,
    *:before {
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      -webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
      -moz-box-sizing: border-box;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }

    .container {
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      position: relative;
      display: block;
      gap: 24px;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 32px;
    }

    .card {
      position: relative;
      display: block;
      margin: auto;
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 4px;
      width: 512px;
      padding: 24px 32px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .logo {
      position: relative;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .logo>img {
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      object-fit: contain;
    }

    .logo>h4 {
      height: 48px;
      line-height: 48px;
      font-family: 'Lexend', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol";
      padding-left: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #101524;
      display: inline-block;
      vertical-align: bottom;
      top: 0;
    }

    .title {
      position: relative;
      display: block;
      color: #101524;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .title>h2 {
      font-family: 'Lexend', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol";
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #101524;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .title>p {
      font-family: 'Lexend', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol";
      font-weight: 200;
      color: #101524;
      opacity: .8;
    }

    .actions {
      position: relative;
      display: block;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .actions>.button {
      position: relative;
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #101524;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .actions>.button>a {
      position: relative;
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
      font-family: 'Lexend', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol";
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 16px 32px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .footer {
      position: relative;
      display: block;
      font-family: 'Lexend', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol";
      font-weight: 200;
      color: #101524;
      opacity: .8;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .footer>p {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .footer>a {
      color: #101524;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="logo">
        <img src="{{src}}" alt="logo-lumilock">
        <h4>{{appName}}</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="title">
        <h2>Changer votre mot de passe ?</h2>
        <p>
          Vous avez fait une demande de réinitialisation de mot de passe
          sur le site {{appName}}. Si ce n&apos;est pas le cas ignorez cet email.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="actions">
        <div class="button">
          <a href="{{token}}">Nouveau mot de passe</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Envoyé grâce à Lumilock pour {{appName}}</p>
      <a href="{{frontUrl}}">{{appName}}</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>